title: Stranger Things: SeasTrend 4 6/1: Johnny Depp, Sheryl Sandberg, Liam Payne, Elon Musk, Kate Bush, Pride Month
itunes:title: Stranger Things: SeasTrend 4 6/1: Johnny Depp, Sheryl Sandberg, Liam Payne, Elon Musk, Kate Bush, Pride Month
description:
In this edition of Stranger Things: SeasTrend 4, Jack and super producer Becca discuss the verdict in the Depp/Heard trial, Sheryl Sandberg leaving Meta, Liam Payne's hot takes on Logan Paul's podcast, Elon Musk trying to force in-office work, Kate Bush charting again due to 'Stranger Things', and the corporatization of Pride Month.

See omnystudio.com/listener for privacy information.
